import {Card, CardContent, Grid, Typography} from '@mui/material'

export default function TaskForm() {
  return (
    <Grid container direction='column' alignItems='center' justifyContent='center'>
      <Grid item xs={3}>
        <Card sx={{mt:5}} >
          <Typography>
            Create Task
          </Typography>
          <CardContent>
            
          </CardContent>
        </Card>
      </Grid>
    </Grid>
  )
}
